&lt;Union Miniere SA> said in a statementthat it has acquired an eight pct interest in PancontinentalMining Ltd &lt;PANA.S> for a sum equivalent to 1.2 billion Belgianfrancs.    Pancontinental operates gold and coal mines in Australiaand natural gas and oil fields in Canada.    Union Miniere said the location of its interest within thePancontinental group will be decided later. It did notelaborate.    Union Miniere is a wholly owned subsidiary of SocieteGenerale de Belgique &lt;BELB.BR>. REUTER&#3;